result.name: Second bite seafood bar & grill 吃多啖

reviews.text:
Second Bite is a cafe/restaurant with fancy modern art as interior decoration which got my heart immediately once I entered it. 

Facing this picture of cutey cat, my first thought was, what a nice reminder! Focus on your meal instead of your phone. Mindful eating. Shortly after that I realized why this picture was placed deep inside the restaurant, it’s because there is really weak signal reception! You can’t upload an IG story nor receive/send a whatsapp message…So forget about your phone while you are in this restaurant… 

This Homemade Minced Pork Burger is massive!!! I adore the minced pork dearly. It’s like the one you have in traditional Chinese restaurants as a dinner dish. Yet it went so well in a burger, especially with molten cheese dripping on and around it. The chips were nice too, I like the potato ones more than the sweet potato ones though. The burger is really big. I could barely manage to finish it and the fries, so I left all the salad untouched… I felt a bit sorry for wasting food, but there was absolutely no more room in my stomach…

I added a house coffee to go with the meal. The coffee was rather disappointing, as the staff used cold milk to make it…It was served lure warm, which was a bit awkward to me.

Side note, ventilation inside the restaurant was really poor. My hair, clothes and bag were all soaked with the smell of cooking. Also, I guess my seat was quite near the toilet, and I could smell some disgusting human waste from time to time, which wasn’t really desirable when you are having a meal…

It’s always a pleasant experience eating there. Food is always delicious, no matter it’s lunch set or coming for dinner.

Last time I went there for dinner and ordered ‘jumbo steak’ and I thought jumbo meant ‘a bit bigger than usual’ but in fact it’s A LOT BIGGER than usual!!!

Of cos I couldn’t finish it in one go so that I took away. And I had steak for another two days 🤣🤣🤣🤣
Hot dishes is tasty.  Cake just so so.  Service haha...

Great food and atmosphere. The lunch sets we had the last few times are all delicious and such good value. The place is great for chilling and hanging out with friends. Will definitely come back if we are closeby.

Lovely cosy restaurant nearby Yuen Chau Plaza, nesrest ATM for HDBC. The decoration inside is colorful, art paintings. TV LCD display, Open kitchen, grill place, seeing chefs preparing your meal.
Angus steak is what I ordered.
Price range : 120 to 200 per person. Recommend Lobster and steak cubes. or Angus Sirloin US steaks. If you like coffees, with fancy choices, eg, rose latte coffee. Bread is french croisants.

reviews.text:

Side note, ventilation inside the restaurant was really poor. My hair, clothes and bag were all soaked with the smell of cooking. Also, I guess my seat was quite near the toilet, and I could smell some disgusting human waste from time to time, which wasn’t really desirable when you are having a meal…

與好友兼街坊得知這店新推出鐵板餐，大份抵食，便相約放工後一起Dinner~

先點了一份小食:
鹹蛋黃金雞翼(6隻)，即叫即炸，熱辣香口，雞皮金黃酥脆，佈滿鹹蛋黃醬，富濃厚蛋黃香，鹹香惹味，雞肉嫩滑多汁，非常入味，齒頰留香，必食!

再點了頂級巨型牛肩肉眼扒餐:
是日餐湯及餐包，南瓜忌廉湯，溫熱暖和，香滑甘甜，與外脆內軟的牛角包配搭合襯~

巨型牛肩肉眼扒，份量十足，入口軟腍，肉汁澎湃，油花豐富，油潤甘香，淋上黑松露汁，味道更濃厚，配菜西蘭花及粟米中和油膩感，南瓜/原味薯條則增添飽肚感，豐盛味美~

蘋果汁，富酸酸甜甜的蘋果味，冰涼止渴，消滯解膩~ 原價$22，跟餐加配只需$8，抵飲!

小食及主餐即叫即做，濃惹味美，滋味十足，而且大份抵食，兩個人share食很飽足~
環境乾淨舒服，食物種類創新味道唔錯！值得一試
訂了枱情人節食飯，一開始落單時要海鮮拼盤，青口敏感想轉唔轉得，叫情人節套餐最小要兩份，咁散叫一個扒和意粉，落好單，店員又走出來話每位要收$300 min charge, 由訂枱開始電話溝通過3次都沒有說，放低餐牌又沒有講，反問他們為何從未提過，店員說門外邊有寫明！想食夠600唔難，但服務態度差！最後去附近日本餐廳食。
環境惡劣，服務極差，性價比超低，但竟有這麼多好評，未免太假了吧，這樣的價錢，太多更好選擇，一定不會再去
